<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Game Teks Prosedur – Kelas 2 SD</title>
<style>
  @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Fredoka+One&family=Nunito:wght@700;800&display=swap');

  * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

  body {
    background: #0f172a;
    font-family: 'Nunito', sans-serif;
    color: white;
    min-height: 100vh;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 24px 16px;
  }

  /* Background stars */
  body::before {
    content: '';
    position: fixed;
    inset: 0;
    background-image:
      radial-gradient(1px 1px at 15% 25%, rgba(255,255,255,0.25) 0%, transparent 100%),
      radial-gradient(1px 1px at 65% 10%, rgba(255,255,255,0.2) 0%, transparent 100%),
      radial-gradient(1.5px 1.5px at 85% 55%, rgba(255,255,255,0.3) 0%, transparent 100%),
      radial-gradient(1px 1px at 35% 75%, rgba(255,255,255,0.2) 0%, transparent 100%),
      radial-gradient(1px 1px at 5%  65%, rgba(255,255,255,0.25) 0%, transparent 100%),
      radial-gradient(1px 1px at 92% 35%, rgba(255,255,255,0.2) 0%, transparent 100%),
      radial-gradient(1px 1px at 50% 90%, rgba(255,255,255,0.15) 0%, transparent 100%);
    pointer-events: none;
    z-index: 0;
  }

  header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 28px;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    animation: fadeDown 0.6s ease;
  }

  @keyframes fadeDown {
    from { opacity:0; transform: translateY(-16px); }
    to   { opacity:1; transform: translateY(0); }
  }

  .logo {
    font-family: 'Fredoka One', cursive;
    font-size: clamp(26px, 5vw, 46px);
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #38bdf8, #a78bfa);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-clip: text;
    line-height: 1.1;
  }

  .subtitle {
    font-size: clamp(12px, 2vw, 15px);
    color: #94a3b8;
    margin-top: 6px;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  }

  .badges {
    display: flex;
    gap: 8px;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    margin-top: 12px;
  }

  .badge {
    background: rgba(56,189,248,0.12);
    border: 1px solid rgba(56,189,248,0.3);
    border-radius: 99px;
    padding: 4px 14px;
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #38bdf8;
    letter-spacing: 0.03em;
  }

  /* Iframe wrapper */
  .iframe-wrap {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 820px;
    background: #1e293b;
    border: 2px solid rgba(56,189,248,0.25);
    border-radius: 24px;
    overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow:
      0 0 0 1px rgba(255,255,255,0.05),
      0 24px 64px rgba(0,0,0,0.5),
      0 0 80px rgba(56,189,248,0.08);
    animation: fadeUp 0.7s ease 0.2s both;
  }

  @keyframes fadeUp {
    from { opacity:0; transform: translateY(24px); }
    to   { opacity:1; transform: translateY(0); }
  }

  /* Top bar like a browser */
  .iframe-topbar {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
    padding: 14px 20px;
    background: #0f172a;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.07);
  }

  .dot {
    width: 12px; height: 12px;
    border-radius: 50%;
  }
  .dot.red    { background: #f87171; }
  .dot.yellow { background: #fbbf24; }
  .dot.green  { background: #4ade80; }

  .url-bar {
    flex: 1;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 6px 14px;
    font-size: 12px;
    color: #64748b;
    margin-left: 8px;
    font-family: monospace;
    white-space: nowrap;
    overflow: hidden;
    text-overflow: ellipsis;
  }

  iframe {
    display: block;
    width: 100%;
    height: 480px;
    border: none;
  }

  /* Info row */
  .info-row {
    display: flex;
    gap: 12px;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    margin-top: 24px;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    animation: fadeUp 0.7s ease 0.4s both;
  }

  .info-card {
    background: #1e293b;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 14px 20px;
    text-align: center;
    min-width: 110px;
  }

  .info-card .ic { font-size: 24px; margin-bottom: 6px; }
  .info-card .il {
    font-size: 11px;
    color: #64748b;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    margin-bottom: 2px;
  }
  .info-card .iv {
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: #f1f5f9;
  }

  /* Tip box */
  .tip-box {
    margin-top: 20px;
    max-width: 820px;
    width: 100%;
    background: rgba(251,191,36,0.08);
    border: 1px solid rgba(251,191,36,0.25);
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 14px 20px;
    font-size: 13px;
    color: #fbbf24;
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 10px;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    animation: fadeUp 0.7s ease 0.5s both;
  }

  footer {
    margin-top: 28px;
    font-size: 12px;
    color: #334155;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    text-align: center;
  }

  /* Fullscreen btn */
  .btn-fullscreen {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #38bdf8, #a78bfa);
    border: none;
    color: #0f172a;
    font-family: 'Fredoka One', cursive;
    font-size: 15px;
    padding: 10px 24px;
    border-radius: 99px;
    cursor: pointer;
    margin-top: 16px;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    transition: transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;
    box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(56,189,248,0.25);
    animation: fadeUp 0.7s ease 0.6s both;
  }
  .btn-fullscreen:hover {
    transform: scale(1.05);
    box-shadow: 0 10px 28px rgba(56,189,248,0.35);
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<header>
  <div class="logo">🎮 Game Teks Prosedur</div>
  <div class="subtitle">SD Islam Tunas Cendekia · Kelas 2 · BAB 7</div>
  <div class="badges">
    <span class="badge">🔀 Unjumble</span>
    <span class="badge">📋 Teks Prosedur</span>
    <span class="badge">🧼 Mencuci Tangan</span>
  </div>
</header>

<div class="iframe-wrap">
  <div class="iframe-topbar">
    <div class="dot red"></div>
    <div class="dot yellow"></div>
    <div class="dot green"></div>
    <div class="url-bar">wordwall.net · Urutkan cara mencuci tangan</div>
  </div>
  <iframe
    src="https://wordwall.net/embed/cf6bc20659d744fbb2fa6d671af402e3?themeId=45&templateId=72&fontStackId=0"
    width="500"
    height="380"
    frameborder="0"
    allowfullscreen
    style="width:100%; height:480px;">
  </iframe>
</div>

<button class="btn-fullscreen" onclick="goFullscreen()">⛶ Layar Penuh</button>

<div class="info-row">
  <div class="info-card">
    <div class="ic">📖</div>
    <div class="il">Mata Pelajaran</div>
    <div class="iv">Bahasa Indonesia</div>
  </div>
  <div class="info-card">
    <div class="ic">🏫</div>
    <div class="il">Kelas</div>
    <div class="iv">2 SD · Fase A</div>
  </div>
  <div class="info-card">
    <div class="ic">📝</div>
    <div class="il">Materi</div>
    <div class="iv">Teks Prosedur</div>
  </div>
  <div class="info-card">
    <div class="ic">🎯</div>
    <div class="il">Mode Game</div>
    <div class="iv">Unjumble</div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="tip-box">
  💡 <span><strong>Tips Smart TV:</strong> Gunakan tombol remote untuk drag & drop kata. Klik START untuk memulai, lalu susun kata-kata menjadi langkah yang benar!</span>
</div>

<footer>
  SD Islam Tunas Cendekia · Cantika Rofiqoh Azhar, S.Pd · TA 2025/2026
</footer>

<script>
function goFullscreen() {
  const iframe = document.querySelector('iframe');
  if (iframe.requestFullscreen) iframe.requestFullscreen();
  else if (iframe.webkitRequestFullscreen) iframe.webkitRequestFullscreen();
  else if (iframe.mozRequestFullScreen) iframe.mozRequestFullScreen();
}
</script>
</body>
</html>
